  <body>
    <h1>Moses' Commandments</h1>
    <ol>
      <li>I am the LORD thy God.</li>
      <li>No other gods before me. No graven images or likenesses.</li>
      <li>Not take the LORD's name in vain.</li>
      <li>Remember the sabbath day.</li>
      <li>Honour thy father and thy mother.</li>
      <li>Thou shalt not kill.</li>
      <li>Thou shalt not steal.</li>
      <li>Thou shalt not bear false witness against thy neighbor.</li>
      <li>Don't covet.</li>
    </ol>
    <hr/>
    <h1>Gaianist Disciplines</h1>
    <ol>
      <li>Love and do as you will.</li>
      <li>God is all life.</li>
      <li>Speak truth.</li>
      <li>Don't aggress.</li>
      <li>Don't kill.</li>
      <li>Don't steal.</li>
      <li>Don't bear false witness.</li>
      <li>Breathe.</li>
      <li>Respect property.</li>
      <li>Record as much as possible.</li>
    </ol>
    <hr/>
    <h1>Signaling</h1>
    <ul>
      <li>Use the <a href='//z13cdn.web.app'>13-sign date</a> for holidays.</li>
      <li>Use the Hijri for the production calendar.</li>
    </ul>
  </body>
